Class FlightCount

  • java.lang.Object
    • FlightCount

  • public class FlightCount
extends java.lang.Object
    This file contains the main class for the Map Reduce Job. This job computes the total number of connections, missed connections and no connections for the entire flight data. This data for the corresponding career and year is then sent to a R script that generated a report based on the given data.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Afan, Abhijeet
